snippet.title: 【Hololive Fan-Made Game】SMOK: Legend of the Laid-Back Heroes
snippet.description:
To prevent the awakening of the Demon Lord, the MC accompanied by these four embarked on a very absurd adventure. Be sure to check out the game link down below.

https://ryjael.itch.io/smok-legend-of-the-laid-back-heroes

Note: This is a fan-made game created in accordance to Cover Corp's Fan-Work Guidelines.
